\section desc Description
Common algorihtm specific for \ref DataFormats_Candidate "Candidate" types
with HepMC generator particle components.

\subsection interface Public interface
None.

\subsection modules Modules
- HepMCCandidateProducer: produces a collection of reco::Candidate with a reco::Track component.
<br><br>
Examples of configuration for the modules is the following:
\htmlonly
<pre>
  module genCandidates = HepMCCandidateProducer {
    string src = "MCFileSource"
    string pdtFileName = "/afs/cern.ch/cms/external/lcg/external/HepPDT/2.02.02/slc3_ia32_gcc323/data/PDG_mass_width_2004.mc"
    bool stableOnly = true
    vstring excludeList = { "nu(e)0", "nu(mu)0", "nu(tau)0", "mu-", "K(L)0", "n0" }
  }
</pre>
\endhtmlonly

